      "patchset_number": 5,
      "line": 62,
      "message": "This condition will be always false as explained here: https://docs.oracle.com/javase/8/docs/api/java/lang/Enum.html#valueOf-java.lang.Class-java.lang.String-. If the `featureName` happens to be invalid an exception will be thrown. Please handle this case.",
